description:
It's a special song pack including 6 popular arrangements of Touhou songs, plus 6 challenges to go with each song!! This pack includes new artists, GET IN THE RING and TUMENECO!

This pack includes the following content.

■6Songs
・Last Devil's Little Sister Flandre S. / Beat Mario
・Game is Over (feat. ytr, Matsu, Rapbit) / TamaOnSen
・PRESERVED VAMPIRE / SOUND HOLIC feat. Nana Takahashi
・Necromantic / Akatsuki Records
・Festival Flame / GET IN THE RING
・Send Stars Round the Sky Faster than the Moon / TUMENECO"

■6 Challenge stages
・Lv4 Shall We Play Together? (Send Stars Round the Sky Faster than the Moon )
・Lv5 Remi's Request (Festival Flame)
・Lv6 Me?! A Training Partner?! (Necromantic)
・Lv6 Bestow Everything Unto Me (PRESERVED VAMPIRE)
・Lv8 Last Devil's Little Sister?! (Last Devil's Little Sister Flandre S.)
・Lv10 I Can't Believe I'm Taking This Game So Seriously! (Game is Over (feat. ytr, Matsu, Rapbit))

*In order to play purchased songs, you need to restart the game after purchase.
name: Special Song Pack Vol. 1
